tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>process documentation</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>internal audit framework</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>management review system</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>corrective action procedures</span></div></div></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardSection\"><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__sectionLabel\">Process</span><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepsRow\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__step\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepNumber\">01</div><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepText\">Gap analysis</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__step\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepNumber\">02</div><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepText\">System design</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__step\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepNumber\">03</div><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepText\">Documentation</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__step\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepNumber\">04</div><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepText\">Staff training</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__step\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepNumber\">05</div><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepText\">Internal audit</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__step\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepNumber\">06</div><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepText\">Certification audit</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__standardCard\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardHeader\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardWatermark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M50 0C50 27.6142 72.3858 50 100 50C72.3858 50 50 72.3858 50 100C50 72.3858 27.6142 50 0 50C27.6142 50 50 27.6142 50 0Z\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-green)\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardTitle\">ISO 22000</h3><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardSubtitle\">Food Safety Management System</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardSection\"><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__sectionLabel\">Goal</span><p class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__goalText\">Implement an internationally recognized food safety management system covering the entire food chain.</p></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardSection\"><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__sectionLabel\">What&#x27;s Included</span><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedList\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>Hazard analysis</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>prerequisite programs</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>FSMS documentation</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>traceability systems</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>emergency preparedness</span></div></div></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardSection\"><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__sectionLabel\">Process</span><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepsRow\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__step\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepNumber\">01</div><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepText\">Current state assessment</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__step\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepNumber\">02</div><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepText\">Hazard identification</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__step\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepNumber\">03</div><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepText\">Control measures</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__step\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepNumber\">04</div><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepText\">System documentation</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__step\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepNumber\">05</div><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepText\">Verification</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__step\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepNumber\">06</div><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepText\">Certification</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__standardCard\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardHeader\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardWatermark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M50 0C50 27.6142 72.3858 50 100 50C72.3858 50 50 72.3858 50 100C50 72.3858 27.6142 50 0 50C27.6142 50 50 27.6142 50 0Z\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-green)\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardTitle\">HACCP</h3><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardSubtitle\">Hazard Analysis &amp; Critical Control Points</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardSection\"><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__sectionLabel\">Goal</span><p class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__goalText\">Identify, evaluate, and control hazards that are significant to food safety at every stage of production.</p></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardSection\"><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__sectionLabel\">What&#x27;s Included</span><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedList\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>Hazard analysis</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>CCP identification</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>critical limits</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>monitoring procedures</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>corrective actions</span></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__includedItem\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__dot\"></div><span>verification protocols</span></div></div></div><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__cardSection\"><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__sectionLabel\">Process</span><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepsRow\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__step\"><div class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepNumber\">01</div><span class=\"QualityStandards-module__tsssWa__stepText\">Team assembly</span></div><div class=\"Qualit